                    <a class="header">What is BandMap?</a>
                    <div class="description">
                        <p>
                            BandMap is a music discovery service. It was written by <a href="https://github.com/TisButMe" target="_blank">me</a>
                            because I wanted to have a tool to visualize which bands were close to my favorites, in a way that would let me see
                            the ones I didn't already know about.
                        </p>
                    </div>
