            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div class="content">
                    <a class="header">What does the size of the circles mean?</a>
                    <div class="description">
                        <p>
                            The radius of each circle is proportional to the artist popularity, according to Spotify.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Note: I'm not using a linear scale: most artists are in the same range of popularity, and using
                            a linear scale wouldn't really display the differences well.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
